      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce an exhilarating 333 hp with a linear power band. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory variable M-differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and recent valve lash adjustments. The chassis retains its signature balance through a finely tuned MacPherson/multi-link suspension setup, providing exceptional turn-in and lateral stability. This is a mechanically sound example, showing the honest patina of a well-loved enthusiast machine while delivering the raw, analog feedback that defines the M-division's golden era.",
